{% set description %}
  Table of Contents can be manually set to sticky position via the <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">sticky</bolt-code-snippet> prop.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
  Additional props are available to adjust the sticky placement in relation to other sticky elements on the same page: <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">scrollOffsetSelector</bolt-code-snippet> and <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">scrollOffset</bolt-code-snippet>.
{% endset %}

